title: Quick Take: New Hampshire Primary Results
description: Donald Trump and Bernie Sanders win decisive victories in the 2016 New Hampshire Primary. What next? This episode: political editor Domenico Montanaro, campaign reporter Asma Khalid, and Brady Carlson of New Hampshire Public Radio join host Tamara Keith. Find the team on Twitter @DomenicoNPR, @asmamk, @BradyCarlson, and @tamarakeithNPR, or at npr.org/politics — or email the show at nprpolitics@npr.org.
